we can find the level of all nodes with respect to the id node and store the videos watched by them and then we can sort them and report the answer

# Approach
for finding the level we can use simple bfs we will use a queue to find level of all nodes and write a check condition if the node is equal to the level given in question then we will store all the vidoes in the map and increase their frequency 

# Complexity
- Time complexity:
O(V+E) for the bfs traversal and for sorting it will be O(VlogV)  

- Space complexity: 
